meta.private_notes: SEA 2nd goal scored on a delayed penalty (against #3 VIC) with the SEA goalie pulled. After goal, ref indicated that #23 VIC (in box on an offsetting penalty) be let out of the box, his penalty removed from the board, and #3 VIC penalty now go on the board.  Noted as an even strength goal (with extra attacker for SEA), but VIC player let out of box after goal.
